{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"85fc358f55","title":"掉念斯诺逝世的暗电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8a2a058722","index":0,"year":1972,"month":2,"day":16,"articleId":"85fc358f55"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"5d37995df1","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"85fc358f55","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"埃德加·斯诺，美国进步作家、记者。1928年第一次到中国。1936年到陕北革命根据地访问，见到了毛泽东等中共和红军的领导人，后写了《西行漫记》等书。新中国成立后，在1960年、1964年、1970年访问中国。1972年2月15日在瑞士病逝。"}],"contents":[{"id":"09a7f90b93","type":"title","text":"惊念斯诺选世的暗电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"85fc358f55"},{"id":"5d37995df1","type":"paragraph","text":"斯诺夫人：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"85fc358f55"},{"id":"ef3aad4f0b","type":"paragraph","text":"获悉埃德加·斯诺先生不幸病进，我谨向你表示沉痛的衰惊和亲切的感问。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"85fc358f55"},{"id":"a6386571ef","type":"paragraph","text":"斯诺先生是中国人民的朋友。他一生为增进中美两国人民之间的相互了解和友谊进行了不解的努力，作出了重要的贡献。他将永远活在中国人民心中。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"85fc358f55"},{"id":"b0022bf808","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"85fc358f55"},{"id":"fd55dd6776","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七二年二月十六日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"85fc358f55"}],"page":{"id":"6c8a2514b4","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"85fc358f55","start":295,"end":295}}}},"__N_SSG":true}